@strong{Welcome to ChaosFight!} Get ready for the most exciting fighting game
adventure on the Atari 2600 Video Computer System!

Have you ever dreamed of choosing your favourite fighter and battling it out with
friends? Now you can! ChaosFight brings fast-paced, action-packed combat right
to your living room TV, with 16 amazing characters to choose from - each with
their own unique personality, fighting style, and special abilities!

@strong{What's an Atari 2600?}

The Atari 2600 (also called the Video Computer System, or VCS) is a classic video
game console from 1977 that plugs into your television. It's like a time machine
that lets you experience gaming the way it was in the golden age! You control
the action with a joystick - a simple stick with a button that feels great in
your hand and responds instantly to your every move.

@strong{What Makes ChaosFight Special?}

ChaosFight is designed to bring out the best in the Atari 2600, with features
that make every match exciting:

@itemize @bullet
@item
@strong{16 Unique Fighters!} From the screen-wrapping Bernie to the flying
Magical Faerie, every character plays differently and has their own surprises!

@item
@strong{Play With Friends!} Challenge up to 3 friends at once for chaotic
4-player battles@footnote{Four-player mode requires a Quadtari adapter - a
special device that lets you plug in four controllers at once!}, or go
head-to-head in classic 2-player duels.

@item
@strong{Real Physics!} Characters jump, fall, and get knocked back when hit -
just like in real fighting! Heavy characters move slower but hit harder, while
light characters zoom around the arena with speed and agility.

@item
@strong{Multiple Arenas!} Choose from 16 different battlegrounds, each with
unique platforms, obstacles, and challenges. Will you fight on open ground,
or leap between platforms?

@item
@strong{Easy to Learn!} The simple joystick controls (up, down, left, right,
and one fire button) mean anyone can start playing in seconds - but mastering
each character's special moves takes practice!

@item
@strong{Looks Great on Any TV!} Whether you have a modern colour TV or a
classic black & white set, ChaosFight is designed to look fantastic.
@end itemize

So grab a joystick, pick your favourite fighter, and get ready to rumble! This
manual will teach you everything you need to know to become a ChaosFight champion!

