This is the classic Atari joystick that probably came with your system! It's a
black stick on a square base with one red button on the upper left corner.

@strong{How to Hold It:}

Hold the controller with the red button in the @strong{upper left}, pointing
toward the TV screen. Rest the base in your palm or on your lap, and use your
thumb or fingers to move the stick.

@strong{How to Use It in ChaosFight:}

@table @strong
@item Moving the Stick
Push the stick in any direction to move your fighter:
@itemize @bullet
@item @strong{LEFT:} Walk/run left, turn to face left
@item @strong{RIGHT:} Walk/run right, turn to face right
@item @strong{UP:} Jump! (height depends on your character's weight)
@item @strong{DOWN:} Guard stance (blocks all damage for up to 1 second)
@item @strong{Diagonals:} UP+LEFT/RIGHT jumps while moving sideways
@end itemize

@item Red Fire Button
Press the button to attack! Your character will perform their signature move:
@itemize @bullet
@item @strong{Melee characters:} Punch, kick, or slash in the direction you're facing
@item @strong{Ranged characters:} Fire a projectile across the screen
@end itemize
@end table

